px"}}},"title":"MXC Token Release Program","post":{"content":"## MXC Token Release Program\n**MXC has chosen to take an unprecedented move towards investor token holdings, we believe that this move is both confident but calculated, bold but necessary, and it’s something which will see token decentralisation pushed to the forefront of MXC. This move, we believe, is one that will secure MXC and investors for the long term.**\n![MXC-token-release-program-1-1](https://cms.mxc.org/uploads/MXC-token-release-program-1-1_60b2d65461.png)\n\nThe Crypto world has experienced some tumultuous times, none more than in the last 12 months. At MXC we’ve been witness to a lot of these market changes in a time where “tokens” as a whole are jockeying for both relevance and implementation in an ever-changing world.\n\nMXC has, with a large sense of deliberateness, we’ve chosen to take the alternative approach to the standard Crypto market. We choose to take the road less travelled, always insisting on offering clear, transparent and understandable use cases and a real purpose for the MXC token.\n\nA little over 6 months ago MXC launched on Huobi, MXC’s first Token Exchange, since then we’ve made some sensational ground-breaking deals with the Shanghai Government, we’ve experienced incredible growth, created a high level of understanding with our core MXC supporters and signed with 3 Top 10 Crypto exchanges, free of charge.\n![MXC-token-release-program-2-1-opt1](https://cms.mxc.org/uploads/MXC-token-release-program-2-1-opt1_7de1d675ab.png)\n\nAs part of our continued commitment to our supporters, MXC is looking now to continue our unconventional course, changing the perception of tokenisation and MXC as a whole. As a result, we’re introducing a revolutionary measure, the **MXC TOKEN RELEASE PROGRAM**. By implementing this program, we firmly believe that MXC increases liquidity, market focus and overall decentralisation of the MXC token.\n\nMXC is preparing to release investor locks to both Early and Pre-Sale investors. The entire MXC team believes so strongly in our movement that we’re handing the power back to the investors, for them to individually decide what they choose to do with their investment. Now, as Peter Parker will remind us, with great power comes great responsibility, this is why MXC has implemented an additional reward / sacrifice model as part and parcel of the **MXC TOKEN RELEASE PROGRAM**.\n\nMXC is offering an immediate release of all Early Investor and Pre-Sale Token locks on the 1st of July, 2019. However, for all investors who choose to engage in the Token Release Option a total of 20% of the investors complete invested MXC portfolio tokens will be sacrificed and burnt as a result of the lock release. Using this method, we believe we have reached a fair balance in regards to a reward and sacrifice model.\n\n*This article is by Aaron Wagener, Co-Founder of MXC Foundation.*","date":"July 01, 2019","metaDescription":"MXC has chosen to take an unprecedented move towards investor token holdings, giving investors the chance to opt for early release of their token lock.","video":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0X7Dkffg0g0","slug":"mxc-token-release-program"},"tags":[{"tag":"Investor","slug":"investor"},{"tag":"MXC Token Release","slug":"mxc-token-release"},{"tag":"MXC Timelock","slug":"mxc-timelock"},{"tag":"Unlock","slug":"unlock"}],"author":{"author":"MXC Foundation","slug":"mxc-foundation"},"zhch_post":{"post":{"slug":"mxc极域通证释放计划"}},"zhtw_post":{"post":{"slug":"mxc極域通證釋放計劃"}},"ko_post":null},"hans":{"category":{"zhchCategory":"官方发布","zhchSlug":"官方发布"},"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='218'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20218'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M111%2042l-6%209h2c5-3%2011%201%2013%207l1%203%203-6c3-6%203-7%201-7l-7-5c-5-3-6-3-7-1M93%2072L81%2093l-6%209-9-15-10-15-8-1h-9v64h20v-9l1-11c0-4%201-4%207%205l5%209h10l5-10%206-9v6l1%207%201%206%201%206h19v-31l-1-33-7-5-7-4-7%2010m132%2021c-4%204-1%2010%204%2010%203%200%207-3%207-6%200-2-5-6-7-6l-4%202m53%2020c-5%205%202%2013%208%209l3-4c1-6-7-9-11-5'%20fill='%23d3d3d3'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1.834862385321101,"src":"/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10b672/ee604/c8afdd497186006b431ef75450ed95e0.png","srcSet":"/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10b672/69585/c8afdd497186006b431ef75450ed95e0.png 200w,\n/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10b672/497c6/c8afdd497186006b431ef75450ed95e0.png 400w,\n/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10b672/ee604/c8afdd497186006b431ef75450ed95e0.png 800w,\n/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10b672/f3583/c8afdd497186006b431ef75450ed95e0.png 1200w,\n/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10b672/5707d/c8afdd497186006b431ef75450ed95e0.png 1600w","srcWebp":"/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10b672/58556/c8afdd497186006b431ef75450ed95e0.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10b672/61e93/c8afdd497186006b431ef75450ed95e0.webp 200w,\n/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10b672/1f5c5/c8afdd497186006b431ef75450ed95e0.webp 400w,\n/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10b672/58556/c8afdd497186006b431ef75450ed95e0.webp 800w,\n/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10b672/99238/c8afdd497186006b431ef75450ed95e0.webp 1200w,\n/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10b672/7c22d/c8afdd497186006b431ef75450ed95e0.webp 1600w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}},"title":"MXC极域通证释放计划","post":{"content":"## MXC极域通证释放计划\n\n**MXC极域决定采取一个前所未有对于通证投资者的举动。我们对此不仅很有信心，而且也有很精细地推算考虑。大胆是必要的，这是将通证去中心化推到MXC极域前端的重要一步。 我们相信这个举动会长期确保MXC极域以及投资者。**\n\n![MXC-token-release-program-1-1](https://cms.mxc.org/uploads/MXC-token-release-program-1-1_60b2d65461.png)\n\n在过去的12个月中，加密货币领域经历了一些动荡的时期。 在MXC极域，我们见证了市场多样的变化，以及在这不断变化的世界中，通证作为一个整体争夺的相关性和落地应用。\n\nMXC极域经过深思熟虑后，我们选择采用另外一种方法进入标准的加密货币市场。 我们选择走的路较少，但坚持提供清晰、透明和易于理解的使用案例是MXC通证的真正目的。\n\n大约6个月前，MXC极域在MXC极域的第一个通证交易所火币上上市。从那时起，我们与上海政府达成了一些突破性的交易。我们快速地增长，与我们的核心MXC极域支持者建立了更深度的理解，并与三家十大加密货币交易所签约。\n\n![MXC-token-release-program-2-1-opt1](https://cms.mxc.org/uploads/MXC-token-release-program-2-1-opt1_7de1d675ab.png)\n\n作为我们对支持者持续承诺的一部分，MXC极域现在正在寻求继续我们非传统的课程，改变对通证化和MXC极域作为一个整体的看法。 因此，我们正在推出一项革命性措施，即是** MXC极域通证释放计划 **。 通过实施该计划，我们坚信MXC极域可以提高MXC通证的流动性、市场焦点和整体的去中心化。\n\nMXC极域准备向早期和售前投资者们发布投资者锁仓。 整个MXC极域团队坚定地相信我们的行动是正确有意义的：将权力交还给投资者，让他们独自地决定选择如何处理他们的投资。 现在，正如Peter Parker提醒我们的，强大的力量带来了重大的责任，这就是为什么MXC极域已经实施了额外的奖励/牺牲模式来作为 **MXC 极域的通证释放计划**的一部分。\n\nMXC极域将于2019年7月1日提供所有早期投资者与售前投资者早期释放。 然而，对于所有选择参与通证释放选项的投资者而言，大约20％的投资者完成投资的MXC投资组合通证，将因锁定释放而被牺牲和烧毁。 使用这种方法，我们相信我们在奖励和牺牲方面达到了公平的平衡。","date":"July 01, 2019","metaDescription":"MXC极域决定采取一个前所未有对于通证投资者的举动。我们对此不仅很有信心，而且也有很精细地推算考虑。大胆是必要的，这是将通证去中心化推到MXC极域前端的重要一步。 我们相信这个举动会长期确保MXC极域以及投资者。","video":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0X7Dkffg0g0","slug":"mxc极域通证释放计划"},"tags":[{"zhchTag":"定时锁","zhchSlug":"定时锁"},{"zhchTag":"MXC极域","zhchSlug":"MXC极域"},{"zhchTag":"投资者","zhchSlug":"投资者"},{"zhchTag":"MXC极域燃料发布","zhchSlug":"MXC极域燃料发布"},{"zhchTag":"解锁","zhchSlug":"解锁"}],"author":{"author":"\tAaron Wagener","slug":"aaron-wagener"},"enPost":{"post":{"slug":"mxc-token-release-program"}}},"hant":{"category":{"zhchCategory":"官方发布","zhchSlug":"官方发布"},"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='218'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20218'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M111%2042l-6%209h2c5-3%2011%201%2013%207l1%203%203-6c3-6%203-7%201-7l-7-5c-5-3-6-3-7-1M93%2072L81%2093l-6%209-9-15-10-15-8-1h-9v64h20v-9l1-11c0-4%201-4%207%205l5%209h10l5-10%206-9v6l1%207%201%206%201%206h19v-31l-1-33-7-5-7-4-7%2010m132%2021c-4%204-1%2010%204%2010%203%200%207-3%207-6%200-2-5-6-7-6l-4%202m53%2020c-5%205%202%2013%208%209l3-4c1-6-7-9-11-5'%20fill='%23d3d3d3'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1.834862385321101,"src":"/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10b672/ee604/c8afdd497186006b431ef75450ed95e0.png","srcSet":"/static/2b1b6fa8e27fecb3f0d9b2f5aa10